    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You design additional custom arrays for your turret. Select two of the following arrays. Add the selected arrays to your list of available arrays.</p><ul><li><p>2d8 mental damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, mental weapon group</p></li><li><p>2d8 poison damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, dart weapon group</p></li><li><p>2d8 vitality damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, laser weapon group</p></li><li><p>2d8 void damage, range increment 60 feet, tech trait, void weapon group</p></li></ul><hr><p><strong>Special</strong> You can take this feat a second time. When you do, you must select different arrays.</p><p></p>",
      "gm": ""
    },
